  <name>Facefy</name>
  <summary>A simple Vala tool to run Face Recognition</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Facefy is an application that wraps the capabilities of well-known technologies like Dlib and face_recognition using a custom JSON RPC daemon created ad-hoc in Python 3.6+ (named `pyfaces`) and a GTK-based desktop environment.</p>
  </description>
